     <div class="post-2063 page type-page status-publish hentry post page clearfix" id="post-2063"> 
      <h2 class="title">Home</h2> 
      <div class="entry clearfix"> 
       <table width="450" border="1" cellspacing="5px" cellpadding="0px"> 
        <tbody> 
         <tr valign="top"> 
          <td align="center" width="450" height="250px"><img alt="" src="http://cshr.cmb.ac.lk/wp-content/uploads/images/mandate.jpg" align="middle"><p></p> <p style="padding-top: 5px;"><strong>The Centre for the Study of Human Rights is a non-profit educational institution attached to the Faculty of Law, University of Colombo.</strong></p> <p><strong>Its mandate is to conduct and facilitate human rights education and research programmes for the university community and the community at large.</strong></p> <p><strong>Its activities are multi-disciplinary in nature.</strong></p></td> 
         </tr> 
         <tr> 
          <td align="center" valign="top" width="450" height="100px"><img alt="" src="http://cshr.cmb.ac.lk/wp-content/uploads/images/vision.jpg" align="middle"><p></p> <p style="padding-top: 5px;"><strong>To create a nation with a rights consciousness in which the dignity and rights of all people are respected.</strong></p> </td> 
         </tr> 
         <tr> 
          <td align="center" valign="top" width="450"><img alt="" src="http://cshr.cmb.ac.lk/wp-content/uploads/images/mission.jpg" align="middle"><p></p> <p style="padding-top: 5px;"><strong>To be a centre of excellence for human rights education and research using a multidisciplinary approach.</strong></p> </td> 
         </tr> 
        </tbody> 
       </table> 
      </div> 
     </div>
